title: [Outlands Manor, Exterior]
description: A trellis sags against the north side of the manor house, reaching to the second floor.  The wood of the trellis that is visible appears paintless and dull beneath the night sky, but most of it is shrouded in dried leaves that rattle in the wind that sweeps along the hilltop.

A trellis sags against the north side of the manor house, reaching to the second floor.  The wood of the trellis that is visible is paintless and has weathered to a uniform grey, but most of it is shrouded in dried brown leaves that rattle in the wind that sweeps along the hilltop.
